    "fullDescription": "Never wonder who owes what after a trip.\n\nTrivense helps travelers and groups split expenses, track spending, and settle up fast — with expense boards, real-time sync, and smart analytics. Built for India and trusted worldwide.\n\nWHY TRIVENSE\n• Clear boards for every trip, group, or household\n• See who paid what and who owes whom — instantly\n• Budget alerts before you overspend\n• Premium analytics when you need deeper insights\n\nPERFECT FOR\n• Friends splitting vacation and weekend trip costs\n• Roommates tracking rent, utilities, and groceries\n• Families planning holidays together\n• Groups tired of spreadsheet math\n\nFEATURES\n• Expense boards — organize spending by trip, household, or project\n• Split & share — invite others with a share code or email\n• Settle up — fair balances and one-tap clarity\n• Smart analytics — category breakdowns, trends, and comparisons\n• Multi-currency — track in ₹ INR, $ USD, and more\n• Secure cloud sync — private boards for you and your invitees\n\nFREE & PREMIUM\nFree — 1 board, weekly analytics, 3 categories\nPremium — unlimited boards, sharing, advanced analytics, export, ad-free\n\nDownload Trivense free. Split expenses, made easy."
  },
